# Styling & Design Tokens Rules

This project uses **Tailwind CSS v4** and local fonts.

## 1. Tailwind CSS v4 Theme
- Configure global custom variables and utilities in the `@theme` block inside `src/app/globals.css`.
- Key color variables:
  - Rust: `--color-brand-rust` (`#b34624`)
  - Deep Black: `--color-deep-black` (`#0A0A0A`)
  - Pure White: `--color-pure-white` (`#FFFFFF`)

## 2. Typography
- Fonts are loaded locally via `localFont` in `src/app/layout.tsx`.
- CSS Custom Variables:
  - Display Font: `var(--font-display)` (mapped from `NATRONRough-Bold.otf`)
  - Sans-Serif Font: `var(--font-sans)` (mapped from `NATRONRough-Medium.otf`)
- Standard Tailwind usage:
  - Display: `font-display`
  - Sans: `font-sans`

## 3. Key Layout Styles
- Background Concrete Texture: Apply `.bg-stone-texture` class to bodies/containers (renders concrete-wall pattern with `#f4f4f2` base).
- Diagonal Clips (Hero/Header):
  - `.clip-diagonal-header`
  - `.clip-diagonal-reverse`
